Package: digitize
Version: 0.0.4
Date: 2016-08-26
Title: Use Data from Published Plots in R
Authors@R: c( person("Timothée", "Poisot", email = "tim@poisotlab.io",
        role = c("aut")), person("Rene", "Sachse", email =
